# === Staged ORT artefacts we don't commit ===
# BINARY_TAG and resources/BINARY_TAG + resources/REVISION ARE
# tracked — the ones below get produced by Build.rakumod at
# install time and live in $XDG_DATA_HOME, but this catches any
# accidental copies inside the source tree.
/lib/onnxruntime*
/lib/libonnxruntime*
/resources/lib/
/resources/include/
/resources/onnxruntime*
onnxruntime-*/
onnxruntime-osx-*.tgz
onnxruntime-linux-*.tgz
onnxruntime-win-*.zip

